# - NGINX_ENABLE_UPSTREAM_KEEPALIVE: Enable/disable connection keepalive
# - NGINX_UPSTREAM_KEEPALIVE: Number of keepalive connections
# - NGINX_UPSTREAM_OPTIONS: Additional server options (backup, weight, etc.)
#
